{"tid":740222,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"最長身是忙內子瑜 TWICE的實際身高順序","createTime":"2018-07-12T16:34:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-15T06:53:02.000Z","uid":51412,"like":23,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"01b1346d4e37bf4cc42319dd31eb2d1a69461a01","tid":740222,"uid":51412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.insight.co.kr/static/2018/07/12/700/xy051a854l0k8etrkz18.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.insight.co.kr%2Fstatic%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F700%2Fxy051a854l0k8etrkz18.jpg&h=4333baf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12日下午，Twice通過Naver Vlive公開了新曲《Dance The Night Away》封面的拍攝現場。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE成員歡快地進行了拍攝。<br />\n<br />\n沒有外貌上漏洞的TWICE的團體照也與眾不同。 TWICE展現了9位女神聚集時&ldquo;無法超越&rdquo;的外貌，令現場工作人員感嘆不已。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.insight.co.kr/static/2018/07/12/700/gmck9he7qf3784h5smyz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.insight.co.kr%2Fstatic%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F700%2Fgmck9he7qf3784h5smyz.jpg&h=415f5f9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTWICE成員們在團體照中不穿高跟鞋也表現出了完美的比例。<br />\n<br />\n成員們穿著拖鞋，按照身高順序展現了性感活潑的魅力。<br />\n<br />\n在這個過程中，無意中公開了身高的順序，吸引了人們的視線。<br />\n<br />\n最矮的成員是身高159cm的彩瑛，最高的成員是預想中的&ldquo;忙內&rdquo;子瑜。子瑜的身高是170cm。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.insight.co.kr/static/2018/07/12/700/e43xfz800krc9l2974g8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.insight.co.kr%2Fstatic%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F700%2Fe43xfz800krc9l2974g8.jpg&h=9fae04c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜之後是定延、Sana、娜璉、MOMO、Mina、志效、多賢。"},{"pid":"7ea3ee65bb2ba7f27098bb4436f8cf8fb1a61d23","tid":740222,"uid":52073,"like":42,"dislike":63,"score":-21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-12T16:36:00.000Z","msg":"和娜璉做愛很舒服"},{"pid":"2628a8ae9c3345a1248d68692a3b8137d5085557","tid":740222,"uid":142313,"like":42,"dislike":1,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"7ea3ee65bb2ba7f27098bb4436f8cf8fb1a61d23","tid":740222,"uid":52073,"like":42,"dislike":63,"score":-21,"citedB