身高是170cm。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.insight.co.kr/static/2018/07/12/700/e43xfz800krc9l2974g8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.insight.co.kr%2Fstatic%2F2018%2F07%2F12%2F700%2Fe43xfz800krc9l2974g8.jpg&h=9fae04c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n子瑜之後是定延、Sana、娜璉、MOMO、Mina、志效、多賢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-13T09:35:53.000Z","msg":"有冇CHING有呢條片link<br />\n多賢着大露背 背心好sexy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n搞到我扯扯地"}]}